      "content": "idk i feel fine now mostly just tired. i dont really want to sit in a waiting room for hours if it's just stress or something. u think it's worth a trip to the er right now or can i just take some ibuprofen and sleep it off? like is there anything else that could cause a sudden spike like that?",
